Some of it might go to the </span><strong>campaigns of the local politician=
s</strong><span> who pushed approvals through &#8211; all done transparentl=
y and openly in accordance with campaign finance rules, of course &#8211; m=
aking it electorally suicidal to stand in the way of projects with popular =
