60;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26p=
x; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The money and fame, and the fact that building shit=
 is cool again, would help solve the labor shortage. Kids would dream of be=
coming tradespeople instead of sitting at computer screens all day.&#160;</=
p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 20px 0;">Call me a dreamer, but it just might help solve immigration, to=
o, as fans of local construction projects would get sick and tired of losin=
g out to better-resourced rivals because of a lack of talent. They&#8217;d =
